metadata.name: I'm Reinventing Myself
metadata.description:
𝕰𝖌𝖔 𝕴𝖓𝖛𝖊𝖓𝖎𝖊𝖓𝖉𝖎 𝕴𝖙𝖊𝖗𝖚𝖒

As the world engulfs itself in chaos, a world inside is brewing anew. The foundations I've created crumble at the seams. The destruction of my ego is at the very dawn of a new chapter. I'm no longer ashamed to say so, I'm reinventing myself. I'm no longer the person I used to be. At the very core of my being, my beliefs were being challenged. I was at a crossroads, and I had to make a decision; To move forward and break through the barriers that were holding me back, or to crumble under the weight of my own expectations. I've decided to take control of the narrative.

— 𝐎𝐒𝐌𝐎𝐒𝐈𝐒®
